01:19:04,400 --> 01:19:06,400
Now, listen carefully.

865
01:19:07,000 --> 01:19:09,000
Path. Follow path.

866
01:19:10,100 --> 01:19:13,000
Gate. Open gate, through gate, close gate.

867
01:19:13,200 --> 01:19:15,600
Last ferry 6.30, so run, run, run.

868
01:19:15,900 --> 01:19:18,100
Wait! Wait.

869
01:19:18,300 --> 01:19:20,300
I came because of Joshua.

870
01:20:02,100 --> 01:20:06,600
Radar reports two unknown tracks are
penetrating the Alaskan air defence zone.

871
01:20:08,300 --> 01:20:12,000
