925
01:23:52,300 --> 01:23:54,600
Oh, it's all right. I've planned ahead.

926
01:23:55,400 --> 01:23:58,100
We're just three miles
from a primary target.

927
01:23:59,300 --> 01:24:01,400
A millisecond of brilliant light

928
