and we're vaporised.

929
01:24:03,500 --> 01:24:07,600
Much more fortunate than the millions
who'll wander sightless

930
01:24:08,000 --> 01:24:10,300
through the smouldering aftermath.

931
01:24:11,700 --> 01:24:14,100
