944
01:25:10,000 --> 01:25:13,300
You're welcome to stay.
You want to sleep on the floor?

945
01:25:18,000 --> 01:25:20,000
Good night.

946
01:25:22,400 --> 01:25:23,900
Let's get outta here.

947
01:25:34,200 --> 01:25:37,200
Come on. We'll find a boat.
There's gotta be a boat.

948
01:25:54,900 --> 01:25:58,600
Mr President, we've got 48 nuclear subs
closing on the United States.

949
01:25:59,000 --> 01:26:02,300
